<h1>许</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#009900;">xǔ</span><span class=alesi>(xu3)</span> , <span style="color:#000099;">hào</span><span class=alesi>(hao4)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciations of 许 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 许</h2><div class=abo>
